to-Clean and User-Friendly：The top fan is detachable, and the base can be rinsed with water. Our incubator is designed with easy disassembly for convenient cleaning. The straightforward operation makes it user-friendly, allowing anyone, even beginners, to effectively use and maintain the incubator.</p><p><br></p><p>4.Automatic Egg Turner Large Duck Incuabtor：You can set the egg turning countdown time:60-210 mins. Guarantees uniform heat distribution and temperature stability during incubation, significantly increasing hatching rates. Clear window allowing you to monitor egg. It includes an Egg Candler, providing a convenient way to observe embryo development at any time.</p><p><br></p><p>5.Accurate Hatching Day Tracking：Our incubator quipped with a Day display and controller, enabling precise humidity management crucial for successful hatching. The external water inlet allows easy water replenishment without disrupting the incubator''s internal environment.</p><p><br></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://sc04.alicdn.com/kf/H078bf092d3c349ba95ba6e7a08e85932n/202601334/H078bf092d3c349ba95ba6e7a08e85932n.jpg"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://sc04.alicdn.com/kf/H297931e210f747a2a5101945c1d271728/202601334/H297931e210f747a2a5101945c1d271728.jpg"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://sc04.alicdn.com/kf/H626be3dd87f94ca0a926a569d561ab2e4/202601334/H626be3dd87f94ca0a926a569d561ab2e4.jpg"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://sc04.alicdn.com/kf/Hfc22f8027a6f47159efd2a005c501be9D/202601334/Hfc22f8027a6f47159efd2a005c501be9D.jpg"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://sc04.alicdn.com/kf/Ha26de7065a964c19a399223339e99301y/202601334/Ha26de7065a964c19a399223339e99301y.jpg"></span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);"><img src="https://sc04.alicdn.com/kf/H78596a42c28d415b92d25d2c1b60e96cW/202601334/H78596a42c28d41