- Durable construction for years of use
- Designed to prevent egg-eating behavior', 'Perfect for commercial egg producers seeking to maximize production while minimizing labor costs associated with egg collection and cleaning.', 'Ideal for backyard chicken keepers who want to simplify egg collection and ensure clean, unbroken eggs for family consumption.', '1. Remove and wash nesting material monthly
2. Check roll-away mechanism weekly for proper function
3. Disinfect boxes quarterly with poultry-safe cleaner
