- Easy-to-follow diagnostic guide included
- All-natural supplement options included
- Specialized applicators for precise administration
- Extended shelf life for emergency preparedness', 'Essential for commercial operations to quickly address health issues before they impact production or spread throughout the flock.', 'Perfect for hobby farmers who want to be prepared for common health issues without veterinary visits for every minor ailment.', '1. Check expiration dates quarterly
