- Weather protection cover keeps feed dry
- Large capacity reduces filling frequency
- Durable construction for years of service', 'Ideal for commercial operations looking to reduce feed costs through less waste while ensuring consistent feed access.', 'Perfect for backyard flocks where convenience and feed conservation are priorities for the poultry keeper.', '1. Empty and clean weekly to prevent mold
