- Weather resistant for all seasons
- Provides both shelter and outdoor access
- Simple to clean and maintain', 'Ideal for small commercial farms that rotate birds across different areas of pasture while maintaining protection from predators.', 'Perfect for backyard poultry keepers who want to move their chickens around the yard to control pests and provide fresh foraging.', '1. Clean the coop thoroughly every 2-3 weeks
2. Check wheels and moving parts monthly
3. Inspect for damage or wear after extreme weather
4. Oil hinges and latches as needed
5. Replace bedding material regularly', 'تم تصميم عشة الدجاج المتنقلة هذه خصيصًا لمربي الدواجن الذين يقدرون سهولة التنقل والمتانة ورفاهية طيورهم.', '- سهلة النقل إلى أرض جديدة
